title: Howard Stern - 2017 September 05-08 - Phony Phone Call Week [Tdo
description:
Howard Stern Sternthology (Phony Phone Call Week) SEP 07 2017 Thu  (02:41:51)


* Sal’s Original Gary Prank Calls – Long before Sal got hired, he was prank calling Gary to call him a “horse tooth jackass.” (04/08/1996)

* Wack Pack Periscopes – Howard reviews “scopes” from Jeff The Drunk, and Medicated Pete. (09/28/2015)

* Jack N Rod With Hearing-Impaired Riley "Huh".

* Jim Breuer - Stern Show guest Jim Breuer stops by and tells Howard stories about his elderly father. (09/07/2011)

* Never Ending Last Name.

* Mad Dog Rant – Howard plays an epic radio rant from Chris “Mad Dog” Russo and the phony phone call it inspired. (03/01/2016)

* Casey Kasem – A tribute to the late/great radio legend complete with Casey’s classic outtakes. (06/16/2014) 

* Richard Calls For Borrowed Porn Movies.

* Robin Speaks Klingon – A new prank call featuring drops of Robin speaking in the "Star Trek" language. (01/13/2014)

* Van Halen Drama – Caller wonders if the band will make it through their tour without breaking up. (06/23/2015)

* Scoresman Got A Tattoo.

* Elephant Man Call – Like Michael Jackson before him, Howard calls a London hospital to bid on the remains of John “The Elephant Man” Merrick. (06/19/1987)

* Swap Shop (Curly Pubes).

* Mel B Phony Phone Call - Clips of the "America's Got Talent" judge are used to make a prank call. (10/07/2013)

* Movie Trivia Swap Shop.
_____________________________________________________________________________

Howard Stern Sternthology (Phony Phone Call Week) SEP 08 2017 Fri  (02:42:23)


* RIP Crackhead Bob – Howard pays tribute to the late Wack Packer and plays his final phony phone call. (02/01/2016)

* Ben & Ray Call Heating Repair.

* Richard’s Dad Prank Call - Clips of Howard's impression of Richard's dad is used to prank a hillbilly gun show. (05/10/2016)

* Sal Calls A Libyan McDonald's.

* Howard Prank Calls – Howard gets the urge to make some calls with Sal & Richard. (03/05/2014)

* Mitur Binesderty (My Turban Is Dirty)

* Hugh Grant – Actor makes his Stern Show debut. (08/10/2016)

* Korean Clock Repair Lady.

* Various Prank Calls - "Ray Pin Kids", "Tera Dikoff" & "Nervous caller Vomits" & "Hillary Clinton Stuck In An Elevator." (10/19/2015)

* JD Sex Tip – JD debuts his personal sex tips. (05/21/2014)

* Auto-Tune Pizza.

* Phony Phone Call Seminar – Howard wants to create a seminar for brainstorming and executing new phony phone call ideas. (07/17/2013)

* Ronnie's Funeral Announcement
